29:58.774 --> 30:01.137
didn't attend those. Describe the typical A&M 
student when you were here. Where was he from? What

30:08.387 --> 30:09.549
kind of income? What were his basic attitudes? The 
average, he was a well-to-do student.

30:20.665 --> 30:21.506
Country or city? Both.

30:27.014 --> 30:30.820
